query:
INSERT INTO project_repos (id, project_id, repo_id)
               VALUES ($1, $2, $3)
               RETURNING id as "id!: Uuid",
                         project_id as "project_id!: Uuid",
                         repo_id as "repo_id!: Uuid",
                         setup_script,
                         cleanup_script,
                         copy_files,
                         parallel_setup_script as "parallel_setup_script!: bool",
                         worktree_cleanup_script
